                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4809,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/31/237301566/8694aaf89d32e75eca416ec7fe41e487_8636855791292057309.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Natlan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Gosoythoth is the heart of the Abyss in the battle with the Natlanese. To defeat the Reaper of the Abyss, the Pyro Archon,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7299,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/12/30/2f098b1f15854fd9dafc54998795a59e_864981592196815761.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Mavuika",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", used the powers of the divine throne, the Ruler of Death, and the six heroes of Natlan. With the Traveler's help, she defeated Gosoythoth and ended the war in Natlan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7298,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Xiuhcoatl",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Gosoythoth is able to corrupt memories contained within the ley lines of the earth, congealing them into tangible forces of catastrophic portent. From these memories, it has managed to extract the remnant will of Xiuhcoatl as the foundation of its own fabricated image. A once-dead dragon was trapped in the final day of its existence, and its boundless fury has consumed all reason.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
